Nollywood actress, Sophia Williams has started the new year in a good note after receiving a Mercedes Benz car as gift from a loved one. Sharing photo of her new car, Sophia who described the car gift as the best way to start the new year said it left her speechless. She wrote: “Best way to start the year, am speechless, it’s a gift.. Got this special gift ..somebody wake me up..damn I love this car. Ayeeee Benz gang.. baddest. Too blessed I can see the future so bright.” See more photos: Source